[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.8.1"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 1.8.1 are now fixed in Tails 1.8.2.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails 1.8.2|news/version_1.8.2]] as soon as possible.

Details
=======

* Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2015-150]], [[!tor_bug 17931]]
* foomatic-filters: [[!debsa2015 3429]]
* libxml2: [[!debsa2015 3430]]
* icedove: [[!debsa2016 3432]]
* samba: [[!debsa2016 3433]]
* linux: [[!debsa2016 3434]]
* git: [[!debsa2016 3435]]
* openssl: [[!debsa2016 3436]]
